@section HeadBlock {
   

}
<div class="fs-lg fw-300 p-5 bg-white border-faded rounded mb-g">

    From this page, you can make a free will donation into our portfolio builder kitty.
    This donation will be distributed to our portfolio builder participants evenly weighted by their share percentage over 30 days (meaning 1/30th will be spent per day on rewards).
