    <br />
    Once the donation is made you will see the ROI% increase <a href="bbp/portfoliobuilder">here.</a>


    <br />
    <br />
    <div class="fs-lg fw-300 p-5 bg-white border-faded rounded mb-g">
        <div class="panel-container show">
            <div class="panel-content">

                Donation Amount:
                <br />
                <input id="txtDonationAmount" style="width:300px;" class="form-control" />
                <button id="btnSubmit" class="btn-default" onclick="DoCallback('portfoliobuilder_donation');">Submit Donation</button>

                <br />
                <br />
                <br />
            </div>
        </div>
        </div>
        Active Donations List (Donations made over the last 30 days that still affect the Portfolio Builder ROI%):
        <br />

        @Html.Raw(ViewBag.ActiveDonations)

    </div>
